---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'SnsPublisher Privacy Policy | KokomaSoft';
const description =
  'Privacy Policy for SnsPublisher, KokomaSoft social content publishing support service.';
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonicalPath="/sns-publisher/privacy/"
  xDefaultPath="/sns-publisher/privacy/"
  ogType="article"
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">SnsPublisher Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: May 18, 2026</p>
      <p class="intro">
        This Privacy Policy explains how KokomaSoft handles information when users access SnsPublisher, our service for preparing and publishing short-form promotional content to authorized creator accounts.
      </p>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>1. Information We May Process</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on the features you use and the permissions you grant, KokomaSoft may process account identifiers, profile information made available through authorization, content or media you choose to publish, captions and metadata you provide, app usage events, device and browser information, error logs, and support messages.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use information to provide requested features, authenticate authorized connections, prepare or transmit content you choose to publish, maintain service security, troubleshoot issues, respond to support requests, comply with legal obligations, and improve KokomaSoft services.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>3. Third-Party Authorization and Permissions</h2>
        <p>
          If SnsPublisher asks you to authorize access to a third-party account, the permission screen will describe the access requested. We only use authorized account information for the feature you requested and in accordance with applicable developer requirements, including TikTok Content Posting API requirements where applicable.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell personal information. We may share information with service providers that help operate SnsPublisher, with connected platforms when you request a publishing action, when required by law, or when needed to protect users, KokomaSoft, connected platforms, or the public from fraud, abuse, or security threats.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>5. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
        <p>
          We retain information only for as long as needed to provide the service, maintain security, resolve disputes, comply with legal obligations, or support legitimate business operations. You may request deletion of KokomaSoft-held information by contacting us at the email below.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>6. Security</h2>
        <p>
          We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information. No online service can guarantee perfect security, so you should avoid submitting sensitive information unless it is necessary for the feature you are using.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>7. Children</h2>
        <p>
          SnsPublisher is not directed to children. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children through SnsPublisher.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>8. International Processing</h2>
        <p>
          KokomaSoft may process information in countries where we or our service providers operate. We take steps intended to handle information consistently with this policy and applicable legal requirements.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in SnsPublisher, platform developer requirements, legal obligations, or security practices. The updated policy will be posted on this page with a new last updated date.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions or deletion requests, contact KokomaSoft at <a href="mailto:kokomasoft@gmail.com">kokomasoft@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .legal-page .container {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }

  h1 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro,
  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.82;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }

  .legal-section {
    padding-top: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
